formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
Notes: 						
1 This certificate has been issued on the basis of verification of unaudited books of accounts of the project upto 30.11.2022.					
2 M/s Care Construction has entered into a development agreement with Mr. Vipul Harshdray Jani on 06.09.2018 inrespect of development of land for a project  for a consideration of Rs. 73,35,600/- in accordance with the terms and conditions mentioned in development agreement. Mr. Vipul Harshadray Jani has made the sale deed in respect of 5 units by collecting aggregate of Rs. 24,03,700/- from various allotees in respect of 5 units before entering into the development agreement with the promoter. The promoter has not received these amount from allotees directly and therefore the same has not been considered as amount received in respect of booked units for the purpose of deposit of the same in separate RERA Bank account of the project although the same is forming part of annexure to form 3, as amount collected in respect of booked units.					
3 Accordingly, as on 30.09.2022 promoter has received Rs. 7,07,01,920 /- from new allotees, other than the allotees as mentioned in para 2 above, which has been deposited in a separate RERA account maintained for the project.					
4 The estimated cost of project as per column no A of 1(ii)(a)(iii), (b) and   has been taken on the basis of estimates made by management.					
5	KYC Details and Mobile Number of Allotees has been provided by the management and the same has not been verified by us.					
6	The system does not allow the excess cost incurred and paid against the estimated cost of construction. Therefore, actual construction cost incurred and paid as on 30.11.2022 is Rs. 5,73,87,652/- whereas the system restrict the cost of construction incurred and paid to the extent of estimated cost of construction only. Therefore, there is difference between actual construction cost incurred and paid as per actual and as per form-3 as on 30.11.2022.					
7 The system does not allow the excess expenditure incurred and paid against the estimated on-site expenditure. Therefore, actual on-site expenditure incurred and paid as on 30.11.2022 is Rs. 73,62,106/- whereas the system restrict the on-site expenditure incurred and paid to the extent of estimated on-site expenditure only. Therefore, there is difference between actual on-site expenditure incurred and paid as per actual and as per form-3 as on 30.11.2022.
